    <item>
      <title>Gitifier 1.3</title>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <html>
            <head>
              <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8">
              <title>Gitifier 1.3</title>
              <link href="http://github.com/psionides/gitifier/raw/master/Sparkle/appcast.css"
                type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" media="all">
            </head>

            <body>
              <br>
              <h3>Version 1.3:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><b>Warning: Snow Leopard is now required.</b></li>
                <li>updated Growl SDK - fixes problems with Growl 1.3</li>
                <li>option to limit number of notifications in one batch</li>
                <li>added history of recent commit notifications to the top bar menu</li>
                <li>fixed 'windows on top' option hiding the menu bar icon on Lion</li>
                <li>fixed crash if git path is incorrect</li>
                <li>fixed problem with truncated output from Git which caused missing commits or git path issues</li>
              </ul>
            </body>
          </html>
        ]]>
      </description>
